_xResult.title: Set Above the Rest
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made dress and legging set with turtle-neck necline
_xResult.longdesc:
A winter set fit for a queen, this custom made two-piece comes with an elegant maxi dress and super comfortable leggings underneath. You’ll be warm and without a worry in the world thanks to the pure cotton knitting, thumb-holes on the sleeves and turtle-neck neckline.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
